name: FORTUNE
description:
Fortune favours the brave. 

Genderless and empowered, this one-of-a-kind statement ring featured a 37.25 carat emerald cut D flawless diamond centre stone flanked by 18 baguette diamonds weighing more than 10 carats, and emerald stone accents. 

This work is comprised of two parts: a 360 degree digital jewelry piece, as well as the design files required to have the piece physically fabricated, should the collector desire. By providing these two components the owner has the assurance that another piece, either digitally or physically, will not be created by anyone else. 

If physically fabricated, this piece would have an estimated worth of more than 5 million USD.
